'''朴智宣'''（{{Lang-ko|박지선}}，{{bd|1984年|11月3日|2020年|11月2日|catIdx=Park}}）是[[韩国|韩国]]知名[[喜剧演员|喜剧演员]]。2020年11月2日，朴智宣去世，享年35岁，疑似[[自殺|自殺]]。

==簡介==
生于[[仁川廣域市|仁川廣域市]][[富平區|富平区]]。<ref>{{Cite web |title=박지선 父, 딸 악플에 직접 남긴 글 재조명 |url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/018/0004492505 |accessdate=2020-11-15 |author=김소정 기자 |date=2019-10-16 |publisher=이데일리 |language=ko |archive-date=2020-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201104103120/https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/018/0004492505 |dead-url=no }}</ref>她畢業於名校[[高麗大學|高麗大學]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=이대출신 곽현화ㆍ고대출신 박지선 … "학력위조 한적 없어요"|url=https://www.hankyung.com/life/article/2007122427247|accessdate=2020-11-02|date=2007-12-24|work=hankyung.com|language=ko|archive-date=2020-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201104103150/https://www.hankyung.com/life/article/2007122427247|dead-url=no}}</ref>2007年，朴智宣通过[[韓國廣播公司|韓國廣播公司]]第22届喜剧演员選秀節目出道。她在[[搞笑演唱會|搞笑演唱會]]中首次亮相，并在2007年获得[[KBS演藝大獎|KBS演藝大獎]]新人奖。<ref>{{Cite news|author=|first=|date=|title=Also from Ewha University and ancient times… KBS 22nd newcomer comedian selection|work=|url=https://www.nocutnews.co.kr/news/268219|accessdate=|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109031537/https://www.nocutnews.co.kr/news/268219|dead-url=no}}</ref>朴智宣在喜劇中經常扮演[[相親|相親]]、約會中屢遭拒絕的女性<ref>{{cite news |title=韩国女谐星朴智宣惊传逝世 与母亲陈尸家中 |url=https://www.rfi.fr/cn/contenu/20201102-%E9%9F%A9%E5%9B%BD%E5%A5%B3%E8%B0%90%E6%98%9F%E6%9C%B4%E6%99%BA%E5%AE%A3%E6%83%8A%E4%BC%A0%E9%80%9D%E4%B8%96-%E4%B8%8E%E6%AF%8D%E4%BA%B2%E9%99%88%E5%B0%B8%E5%AE%B6%E4%B8%AD |publisher=法廣 |accessdate=2020-11-04 |archive-date=2020-11-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201102223851/https://www.rfi.fr/cn/contenu/20201102-%E9%9F%A9%E5%9B%BD%E5%A5%B3%E8%B0%90%E6%98%9F%E6%9C%B4%E6%99%BA%E5%AE%A3%E6%83%8A%E4%BC%A0%E9%80%9D%E4%B8%96-%E4%B8%8E%E6%AF%8D%E4%BA%B2%E9%99%88%E5%B0%B8%E5%AE%B6%E4%B8%AD |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2020年11月朴智宣的父亲联系不上朴智宣和其母亲，於是报警。最終警方在她們位於[[首爾|首爾]][[麻浦区|麻浦区]]的家中被警方发现，已經[[身故|身故]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=韩笑星朴智宣和母亲在家中身亡|url=https://cn.yna.co.kr/view/ACK20201102003800881|accessdate=|author=韓聯社|date=|format=|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128204246/https://cn.yna.co.kr/view/ACK20201102003800881|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Herald">{{Cite web|title=[Breaking] Comedian Park Ji-sun found dead|url=http://www.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20201102000915|accessdate=2020-11-02|date=2020-11-02|work=The Korea Herald|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201102135517/http://www.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20201102000915|archivedate=2020-11-02}}</ref><ref name="Yonhap">{{Cite web|title=(3rd LD) Comedian Park Ji-sun found dead at home: police|url=https://en.yna.co.kr/view/AEN20201102008753315|accessdate=2020-11-02|date=2020-11-02|work=Yonhap New Agency|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201102135728/https://en.yna.co.kr/view/AEN20201102008753315|archivedate=2020-11-02}}</ref>。警方在朴家發現一张纸，推测是朴智宣母亲所寫。据《[[朝鲜日报|朝鲜日报]]》报道，紙條內容是朴智宣母亲透露朴智宣因罹患皮肤病而非常痛苦，而最近朴智宣又患上了其他疾病，在治疗其它疾病的过程中，朴智宣皮肤病恶化，更加痛苦，不能只让女儿一个人離開世界。對自己的丈夫感到抱歉。朴智宣生前患有慢性皮肤病，其皮膚对阳光过敏，無法使用[[化妝品|化妝品]]，並一直在接受治疗<ref>{{Cite web|title=故 박지선, 과거 지병 '햇빛 알레르기'도 개그로 승화해|url=https://news.mt.co.kr/mtview.php?no=2020110219043734791|accessdate=2020-11-02|author=마|first=아라|work=Money Today|archive-date=2020-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201104103312/https://news.mt.co.kr/mtview.php?no=2020110219043734791|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=故 박지선 지병 '햇빛 알레르기', 어떤 질환?|url=http://www.slist.kr/news/articleView.html?idxno=197616|accessdate=2020-11-02|author=Kim|first=Na-yeon|work=Single List|archive-date=2020-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201104103306/http://www.slist.kr/news/articleView.html?idxno=197616|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=36岁朴智宣与母同时死亡‧ 妈妈遗书曝光：女儿得病很痛苦|url=https://www.sinchew.com.my/content/content_2370010.html|accessdate=2020-11-15|author=星洲網|date=|format=|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2020-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201103041146/https://www.sinchew.com.my/content/content_2370010.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。警方怀疑母女死因為自杀。

